file: InMemoryOutboxStore.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Infrastructure\\Storage\\InMemoryOutboxStore"
type: final class
summary: InMemoryOutboxStore provides an in-memory implementation of the outbox pattern for buffering domain events before publication. It ensures event durability within the current process lifecycle by managing entry states and preventing duplicate submissions via sink-based deduplication.
